definitions.definition: A movement made to confuse an opponent ; a dummy .
A blow , thrust , or other offensive movement resembling an attack on some part of the body , intended to distract from a real attack on another part.
Something feigned ; a false or pretend appearance ; a pretence or stratagem .

main_definition: ( often military ) A movement made to confuse an opponent ; a dummy .
secondary_definitions: ( boxing , fencing ) A blow , thrust , or other offensive movement resembling an attack on some part of the body , intended to distract from a real attack on another part.
( figuratively ) Something feigned ; a false or pretend appearance ; a pretence or stratagem .
